              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Natural vanadium and indium materials, 99.99% pure were",
                "used for preparing samples. The samples of vanadium",
                "and indium were deposited on aluminium backing of 6.75-",
                "mg/cm**2 using evaporation technique. The thicknesses",
                "of vanadium and indium deposition were 0.32 and 4.2-mg/",
                "cm**2, respectively."
